  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "This model has been applied in clinical research settings to predict hemolysis in centrifugal blood pumps under ventricular assist device operating conditions. The CFD hemolysis model targets the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed across all 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors; seven factors were formally assessed and six were flagged as epistemic gaps. All assessed factors achieved levels meeting or exceeding required thresholds at Model Risk Level 5, supporting an Accepted decision under the Minimal credibility profile. The intended-use scope is described narratively above; no structured Context of Use object is recorded in this package.",
