      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model selection justified by comparison of k-omega SST, k-epsilon realizable, and RSM on benchmark rotating flow; power-law hemolysis model form uncertainty quantified.",
      "rationale": "Only k-omega SST evaluated; alternative turbulence models not compared. Power-law exponents from Giersiepen 1990 used without assessment of alternative damage model forms. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
